<div class="flex_column av_one_full first  avia-builder-el-6  el_after_av_hr  el_before_av_hr  "><section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><h1 style="text-align: center;">The Law Office of John McDuff, P.C.</h1>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Practicing Business &#038; Tax Law in Austin, Texas</h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">
The Law Office of John McDuff, P.C. in Austin, TX is a solutions oriented firm that works tirelessly to address your business and tax issues. Sole attorney, John McDuff, understands the legal needs of business owners and individuals. With over 20 years of experience practicing exclusively in business and tax law, McDuff has developed the knowledge to help his clients protect their assets. The Law Office of John McDuff, P.C. has assisted clients on cases with up to 25 million dollars at stake, and we excel at providing wise counsel when the stakes are high.</p>
</div></section>
<div style=' margin-top:11px; margin-bottom:30px;'  class='hr hr-custom hr-center hr-icon-yes  avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_textblock  el_before_av_video '><span class='hr-inner   inner-border-av-border-thin' style=' width:47%;' ><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span><span class='av-seperator-icon' style='color:#a5a5a5;' aria-hidden='true' data-av_icon='' data-av_iconfont='entypo-fontello'></span><span class='hr-inner   inner-border-av-border-thin' style=' width:47%;' ><span class='hr-inner-style'></span></span></div>
