<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><h2 style="text-align: center;">An AV Preeminent Rated Lawyer</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">At the Law Office of John McDuff, P.C., our ability to handle business and tax matters for our clients effectively and efficiently has earned the confidence of our clients and peers. John McDuff has earned an AV Preeminent® peer review rating from Martindale-Hubbell (a rating system through which experienced members of the bar and judiciary evaluate their peers). This rating indicates the highest level of performance in legal knowledge, analytical capabilities,<br />
judgment, communication ability, and legal experience.</p>
</div></section></div>
