</div></section>
<div class="flex_column av_one_half first  avia-builder-el-13  el_after_av_textblock  el_before_av_one_half  column-top-margin"><section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><p>By intentionally limiting my practice to business and tax law for over 20 years, I provide creative and effective solutions for the following types of cases:</p>
</div></section>
